#: ../../source/usage.rst:2
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "使用方法"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:5
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:7
msgid ""
"Fabricatio is a streamlined Python library for building LLM applications "
"using an event-based agent structure. It features:"
msgstr "Fabricatio 是一个精简的 Python 库，用于通过基于事件的代理结构构建 LLM 应用程序。它具有以下特点："

#: ../../source/usage.rst:9
msgid ""
"**Event-Driven Architecture**: Robust task management through an "
"EventEmitter pattern"
msgstr "**事件驱动架构**：通过 EventEmitter 模式实现强大的任务管理"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:10
msgid ""
"**LLM Integration & Templating**: Seamlessly interact with large language"
" models and dynamic content generation"
msgstr "**LLM 集成与模板化**：无缝与大型语言模型交互并生成动态内容"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:11
msgid ""
"**Async & Extensible**: Fully asynchronous execution with easy extension "
"via custom actions and workflows"
msgstr "**异步与可扩展性**：完全异步执行，并可通过自定义操作和工作流轻松扩展"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:14
msgid "Basic Example"
msgstr "基本示例"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:16
msgid "Here's a simple \"Hello World\" example:"
msgstr "这里是一个简单的“Hello World”示例："

#: ../../source/usage.rst:49
msgid "Async Usage"
msgstr "异步使用"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:51
msgid "For asynchronous execution:"
msgstr "对于异步执行："

#: ../../source/usage.rst:81
msgid "Delegation Modes"
msgstr "委派模式"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:83
msgid "Fabricatio provides two delegation modes:"
msgstr "Fabricatio 提供两种委派模式："

#: ../../source/usage.rst:85
msgid ""
"``delegate()`` (async, non-blocking): Returns a ``Task`` handle. Use this"
" when you need to run multiple tasks concurrently or want to avoid "
"blocking the event loop."
msgstr "``delegate()``\ （异步，非阻塞）：返回一个 ``Task`` 句柄。当您需要并发运行多个任务或希望避免阻塞事件循环时使用此方法。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:88
msgid ""
"``delegate_blocking()`` (sync): Blocks until the task completes. Use this"
" in synchronous contexts or simple scripts where concurrency is not "
"needed."
msgstr "``delegate_blocking()``\ （同步）：阻塞直到任务完成。在同步上下文或不需要并发的简单脚本中使用此方法。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:91
msgid ""
"Fire-and-forget: You can call ``delegate()`` and discard the result if "
"you only need to trigger the side effect. The task will still be "
"processed by the Role."
msgstr "发射即忘：如果只需要触发副作用，可以调用 ``delegate()`` 并丢弃结果。任务仍会被角色处理。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:94
msgid ""
"Why async matters: Concurrent task execution lets you interleave LLM "
"calls, database queries, and external API requests without blocking the "
"event loop. This is critical for chat loops, streaming responses, and "
"real-time applications where latency must be kept low."
msgstr "为什么异步很重要：并发任务执行可以让您在不阻塞事件循环的情况下交错执行 LLM 调用、数据库查询和外部 API 请求。这对于聊天循环、流式响应以及需要保持低延迟的实时应用程序至关重要。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:100
msgid "Usage Scenarios"
msgstr "使用场景"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:102
msgid "Fabricatio supports various usage scenarios:"
msgstr "Fabricatio 支持各种使用场景："

#: ../../source/usage.rst:104
msgid "Simple Chat"
msgstr "简单聊天"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:105
msgid ""
"Interactive conversational loop. Demonstrates ``Action`` as a stateful "
"chat handler — each turn appends to conversation history, and the "
"workflow persists context across interactions."
msgstr "交互式对话循环。演示 ``Action`` 作为有状态的聊天处理器——每轮对话都会追加到对话历史中，工作流在多次交互间保持上下文。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:109
msgid "Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)"
msgstr "检索增强生成 (RAG)"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:110
msgid ""
"Retrieves relevant documents *before* the LLM call. Shows how "
"``Action``\\ s compose external data (embeddings, vector DB) with "
"generation — the retrieval step feeds context into the prompt step."
msgstr "在 LLM 调用\ *之前*\ 检索相关文档。展示 ``Action`` 如何将外部数据（嵌入向量、向量数据库）与生成相结合——检索步骤将上下文提供给提示步骤。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:114
msgid "Article Extraction"
msgstr "文章提取"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:115
msgid ""
"Parses and injects structured data into vector databases. Demonstrates "
"multi-step pipelines: fetch, parse, chunk, embed, and store — each a "
"separate ``Action``."
msgstr "解析并将结构化数据注入向量数据库。演示多步管道：获取、解析、分块、嵌入和存储——每一步都是一个独立的 ``Action``。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:119
msgid "Propose Task"
msgstr "任务提案"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:120
msgid ""
"LLM-driven task decomposition from natural language. The LLM analyses a "
"user request and breaks it into sub-tasks, each of which can be "
"dispatched as a new workflow."
msgstr "基于 LLM 的自然语言任务分解。LLM 分析用户请求并将其拆分为子任务，每个子任务可以作为新的工作流进行调度。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:124
msgid "Code Review"
msgstr "代码审查"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:125
msgid ""
"Demonstrates the review→correct workflow pattern: review code, collect "
"feedback, then apply corrections in a follow-up action — all within the "
"same workflow."
msgstr "演示审查→修正的工作流模式：审查代码、收集反馈，然后在后续操作中应用修正——全部在同一工作流内完成。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:129
msgid "Write Outline"
msgstr "撰写大纲"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:130
msgid ""
"Demonstrates structured output generation with typst formatting. The "
"``Action`` returns a structured schema that is rendered into a formatted "
"document."
msgstr "演示使用 typst 格式化的结构化输出生成。``Action`` 返回一个结构化模式，被渲染为格式化的文档。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:134 ../../source/usage.rst:173
msgid ""
"For detailed examples and advanced usage patterns, explore the "
"``examples/`` directory in the repository."
msgstr "有关详细示例和高级使用模式，请探索存储库中的 ``examples/`` 目录。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:137
msgid "Key Concepts"
msgstr "关键概念"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:139
msgid "**Actions**"
msgstr "**操作**"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:140
msgid ""
"The basic unit of work in Fabricatio. Each action performs a specific "
"task and can be chained together. *Why:* Encapsulate LLM calls and side "
"effects so they're composable and testable."
msgstr "Fabricatio 中的基本工作单元。每个操作执行特定任务，并可以串联在一起。\ *原因：*\ 封装 LLM 调用和副作用，使其可组合且可测试。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:143
msgid "**Workflows**"
msgstr "**工作流**"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:144
msgid ""
"A sequence of actions that define how tasks are processed. *Why:* Chain "
"actions into deterministic pipelines — each step's output feeds the next."
msgstr "定义任务处理方式的操作序列。\ *原因：*\ 将操作链接为确定性管道——每一步的输出馈入下一步。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:147
msgid "**Events**"
msgstr "**事件**"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:148
msgid ""
"Triggers that initiate workflows. Events follow an event-driven "
"architecture pattern. *Why:* Decouple task submission from execution — "
"the same event can trigger different workflows in different Roles."
msgstr "触发工作流的机制。事件遵循事件驱动架构模式。\ *原因：*\ 将任务提交与执行解耦——同一事件可以在不同角色中触发不同的工作流。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:151
msgid "**Roles**"
msgstr "**角色**"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:152
msgid ""
"Entities that manage workflows and handle task delegation. *Why:* Own "
"workflows and LLM configuration, enabling different agents with different"
" capabilities."
msgstr "管理工作流和处理任务委派的实体。\ *原因：*\ 拥有各自的工作流和 LLM 配置，使不同代理具备不同能力。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:155
msgid "**Tasks**"
msgstr "**任务**"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:156
msgid ""
"Work items that get processed through workflows. *Why:* Carry state "
"through a workflow, track dependencies, and support cancellation."
msgstr "通过工作流处理的工作项。\ *原因：*\ 在工作流中携带状态、跟踪依赖关系并支持取消。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:160
msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr "入门指南"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:162
msgid "Install fabricatio with desired capabilities"
msgstr "安装带有所需功能的 fabricatio"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:163
msgid "Define your actions by subclassing ``Action``"
msgstr "通过继承 ``Action`` 来定义您的操作"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:164
msgid "Create workflows combining your actions"
msgstr "创建组合您操作的工作流"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:165
msgid "Register workflows with roles using events"
msgstr "使用事件将工作流注册到角色"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:166
msgid "Submit tasks for processing"
msgstr "提交任务以进行处理"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:168
msgid ""
"``Task.delegate(event_name)`` dispatches the task to the ``Role`` that "
"owns the matching workflow. The task carries state (``init_context``, "
"``dependencies``) across workflow steps, so each action in the chain has "
"access to previous results."
msgstr "``Task.delegate(event_name)`` 将任务调度到拥有匹配工作流的 ``Role``。任务在工作流步骤间携带状态（``init_context``、``dependencies``），因此链中的每个操作都可以访问之前的结果。"

